##1: CMD;

C:> cd \prog\java_txt
C:> set path=%path%;C:\Program Files\Java\jdk1.8.0_131\bin
C:> javac <insert_file_Name_here>.java
C:> java <insert_file_name_here>

Disclamer: class name and file name must match


##2: Conventions;

Package: com.foo.bar
Class: FooBar
Interface: FooBar
Method: fooBar
Variables: fooBar
Constants: FOO_BAR
